msgstr "顯示聯絡人位置的地圖。"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/geolocation.rst:10
msgid ""
"To use the feature, open the :guilabel:`Settings` app, and, under "
"the :guilabel:`Integrations`, section, activate :guilabel:`Geo "
