"navigation, and recommendations."
msgstr ""
"Google Places API 地圖提供有關地點、商家和興趣點的詳細資訊。它支援基於位置的"
"功能，如搜尋、導航和推薦。"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/geolocation.rst:34
